    "body": "### Problem\n\nI'm seeing the following error happen on `master` when using LSP hover:\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/43f79f37-1334-47b7-96e6-3365cc76fa5d)\n\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nUsing nightly open a Lua file with LuaLS installed. Over any function call invoke LSP hover using the default \"K\" mapping.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nNo errors on hover.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.11.0-dev-1184+gcc6992f1ca\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nNo\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nmacOS 15.0.1\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nghostty\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-ghostty\n\n### Installation\n\nFrom source",
