            "body": "Haven't looked into the details yet, but just wanted to report some of the things I noticed:\n- multi-line completions (using copilot) trigger this issue for me. Single line works fine.\n- something seems off with indentation in nightly, which may (or may not) be related\n\n---\n\nEdit: for that indent:\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/abbb96bb-5520-4dc0-be03-f63f73ed050d)\n\nAt the end of the line `-- test comment`, when I press `o`, the comment below is not indented.\n\nI'm using nvim-treesitter indents, so may be related. I don't use the `comment` parser.\n",
